Summary: A light moving fast with no blinkers like a plane has.
divs: Sighting DetailsIn my kitchen turned toward the east side of my place looking out the window when I saw this light moving quickly but I noticed there were no blinkers like a plane has and moving faster. I called my roommate who was in the living room, but when he came to the window it was gone. Did anyone else see something around this time? It was a yellowish light.
